property.name: GlobalSyncId
property.description: The global unique identifier used to identify this record across applications during sync.

property.name: AppId
property.description: Foreign key to AppIdMapping table. Used to identify the endpoint that last updated this record.

property.name: Tick
property.description: Vector Clock Incrementor. Used by Integration Contract synchronization to identify changes.

property.name: ActiveFlag
property.description: Flag to indicate if the SalesOrder is an 'active' one . Default = True

property.name: PriceListId
property.description: Foreign key relationship to the SlxPriceList table.

property.name: DueDate
property.description: Date the order is due by the Customer. W3C date time standard for XML (ISO 8601). The base timezone is UTC. The offset is included. UTC should be used See the reference here: http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2/#isoformats

property.name: DiscountTotal
property.description: The total value of the discount applied to the order.

property.name: TaxTotal
property.description: The total value of the tax applied to the order.

property.name: IsQuote
property.description: Flag to indicate if this is an Order or a Quote.
